Initial commit - Pong Classic webapp

Classic Pong game for smartphone with touch controls.
Features:
- 1 or 2 player modes
- Touch/drag paddle controls with multi-touch support
- AI opponent for single player mode
- Retro arcade visual style with CRT effects
- Sound effects
- Responsive design for mobile

First to 11 points wins.

